Title: 'Portugal - Back to the Homeland! '
DateModified: '2019-02-09'
DatePublished: '2019-02-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/portugal-back-to-the-homeland
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Tina  Guiomar
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Growing up as a Portuguese-American with the pride of the food, language and\
  \ culture deep engrained. Taking a step back to the Homeland to uncover what the\
  \ locals live about their country. As Portugal becomes the next tourist hotspot\
  \ let\u2019s discover what Portuguese love about their country. Connecting and getting\
  \ to know the people, the places they love, the food they love to eat, secret local\
  \ spots to eat and the natural beauty of the country."
